com.kenticocloud.delivery

Class System

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kenticocloud.delivery.System

  • public class System
extends java.lang.Object
    Content item system attributes

    Every ContentItem and ContentType in a JSON response from the Delivery API contains a system attribute. This attribute represents the System object with information about the retrieved content item
